plot: Mark takes a stand, unaware of the ramifications for his family, the GDA, and even the guardians. Cecil remembers his past and Eve makes an important decision.

It's revealed how in the past, Cecil became head of thew GDA. In the present, Mark and Cecil have a difference of opinion over Cecil calling up some individuals to serve. The Guardians of the Glove split over a difference, and Mark tells Eve his feelings.—Gislef
